# EVM

## Installation

1. Install [foundry](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry)
2. run `npm install`

EVM SDK uses `xcvm-typescript-sdk` library for its tests, however this typescript library is not published it, whenever the library source code is edited, it should be updated here in evm directory by running `npm install --force`


## Run tests
There are 2 set of tests
 - Router and bridge related tests, which are implemented in solidity using `forge`
    - `npm run test` or `forge test` 
 - XCVM program encoding and decoding related tests, which are implemented in typescript using `hardhat`
    - `npm run test-proto` 

